    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Pieces of blotting paper in various sizes and formats, including individual sheets, gatherings of sheets, and large sheets inserted or built into desk pads to protect desk tops from ink stains.</Note_Text>
